    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused example featuring a high-revving naturally aspirated flat-six mated to a precise short-throw manual gearbox. This unit benefits from a recently pinned coolant pipe job and a reinforced IMS bearing for long-term reliability. The suspension has been optimized with adjustable coilovers and stiffer bushings, significantly reducing body roll and sharpening turn-in response. Brakes have been upgraded with stainless steel braided lines and high-friction compound pads for superior modulation and heat dissipation. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression and leak-down numbers\u2014are excellent. This is a visceral, analog machine ready for the canyons or the track.",
